    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Carved wooden ancestor statues, ranging in height up to a meter, of the Oron-Ibibio people in southeastern Nigeria in Africa.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
